stories.text:
Hi guys,
So today my technical co-founder just left due to academic pressure and as he can't commit as much as I want so he just left and my ship's been sailed since the morning. I've been looking for another technical person to join ASAP as we are close to pitch and seek investment as I have connections to VCs but I do need a CTO right now. I've been working on my idea since the last semester and I have even designed everything but the development is the only thing needs to be done. I'm in Montreal and I'm actively seeking for any enthusiast person to join in Canada.
Please let me know as I really am rooted for my idea and it burnt me to my heart when my CTO just left.
thanks
